419
00:27:52,620 --> 00:27:54,100
Maka dia jelas akan bersembunyi.

420
00:27:54,660 --> 00:27:57,380
Kau akan menunggu ditangkap kalau jadi dia?

421
00:27:58,140 --> 00:27:59,940
