567
00:40:52,700 --> 00:40:54,180
Yah, enak, deh.

568
00:40:56,220 --> 00:40:57,620
Ini enak.

569
00:40:57,940 --> 00:40:59,340
Silakan makan sebanyak mungkin.

570
00:40:59,460 --> 00:41:00,900
Baik!

571
00:41:46,540 --> 00:41:47,940
