600
00:44:00,940 --> 00:44:02,340
Saya minta maaf.

601
00:44:04,300 --> 00:44:05,740
Tolong jangan kembali lagi.

602
00:44:11,780 --> 00:44:13,220
Lalu, ...

603
00:44:14,540 --> 00:44:16,580
ketika kami melihat berita bahwa
